# Tests for <%= className %>

This directory contains all tests for the <%= name %> tool package.

## Test Structure

- `_setup.ts` - Global test setup and configuration
- `isolated-tests/` - Unit tests for individual components
- `functional-tests/` - End-to-end functional tests
- `coverage-tests/` - Tests focused on code coverage
- `_reports/` - Test reports and coverage output

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
nx test @fux/<%= name %>

# Run with coverage
nx test @fux/<%= name %> --coverage

# Run specific test types
nx test @fux/<%= name %> --testPathPattern=isolated-tests
nx test @fux/<%= name %> --testPathPattern=functional-tests
nx test @fux/<%= name %> --testPathPattern=coverage-tests
```

## Test Configuration

Tests use Vitest with configuration from:
- `vitest.config.ts` - Main test configuration
- `vitest.coverage.config.ts` - Coverage-specific configuration
